As partner to the lung, the large intestine also affects the skin profoundly
thus many points on the large intestine meridian are used for affecting the
skin of the face. The stomach meridian traverses much of the face and is often
used to obtain local cosmetic effect. It is the yin-yang partner to the spleen
and its points help to tone the flesh (the muscles and the fat underlying
the skin). This communication of the lung and the spleen (zang organs) and
the stomach and the large intestine (fu organs) allows them to act
synergistically.<br>

