about the state of internal organs, a yellow tone can indicate an
energetic deficiency of the spleen, for example. Certain areas of the face
indicate the state of particular organs depending on the brightness and color.
Thus, we see how the face can provide us with relevant information regarding
the body's overall health. Outer beauty depends on the internal energy state,
therefore it is necessary to focus the treatment on balancing energy
which will provide lasting results.<br>
