<h1 class="off">The Mechanism of Acupuncture</h1><br>

As with regular acupuncture, points are chosen according to the individual
and their specific needs at the time of treatment. The
established parameters of diagnosis and treatment strategy will generally
apply when practising cosmetic acupuncture. Many local points on the face and head are also
needled to obtain the extra cosmetic effects.
